public class WaterGroundSurfaceType
extends _WaterBoundarySurfaceType

Type describing the ground surface of a water body, i.e. the boundary to the digital terrain model. As subclass of _CityObject, a WaterGroundSurface inherits all attributes and relations, in particular an id, names, external references, generic attributes and generalization relations.
